headline: Targa Resources Corp. Announces Form 10-K Available
summary: HOUSTON, Feb. 20, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Targa Resources Corp. (NYSE: TRGP) ("TRGP" or the "Company" or "Targa") has filed its Form 10-K with the Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) for the year ended December 31, 2024. The report may be accessed at www.sec.gov. The report is also available in the Investors section of the Company's website at www.targaresources.com, or by going directly to https://www.targaresources.com/investors/financial-information/sec-filings.
